data.description: **PRICE IMPROVEMENT***Unlock the door to your future! Settled along the streets of a quiet neighborhood just minutes from Pride Elementary, Heritage Middle School, and Pine Ridge High School, this four-bedroom, two-bath house welcomes you home. Green grass, easy-to-maintain landscaping, and a covered front entrance usher you inside to high-quality LVP hardwood flooring and recessed lighting. Wander towards the well-appointed kitchen with dark wooden cabinetry, granite counters, stainless appliances, and a large island with enough seating for four bar stools - ideal for cozy dinners. The adjoining dining room with sliding door access to the oversized yard for a backyard oasis and living room offers the perfect setting for entertaining all year long. Additionally, this home boasts a large primary suite, an attached garage, and access to a shared neighborhood pool, a center for relaxation and recreation during the hot summer days. The key to your dream life is in your hands as you make Deltona home! Magnet schools within 30 minutes are Deland High, and Croom's Academy.
